WhisperBack - Send a feedback in an encrypted mail
##################################################

Copyright (C) 2009 Amnesio <amnesia@boum.org>


DESCRIPTION
===========

WhisperBack is a small pyGTK application intend to provide a
user-friendly way to send a GnuPG-encrypted feedback to the amnesia
dev team.


INSTALLATION
============

WhisperBack is packaged using distutils. To install it :
  $ ./setup.py build
and then under root
  # ./setup.py install

USAGE
=====

Please see the man page
